{"title":"Clsx——优雅的CSS类名处理工具","uid":"fa1d9184ca694325f48cf22b078616f3","slug":"clsx-elegant-css-classname-processing","date":"2025-08-06T02:38:26.000Z","updated":"2025-08-06T12:09:22.604Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/clsx-elegant-css-classname-processing.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ProselyteCoding/online-assets/main/blog/cover-css.png","content":"<h1 id=\"Clsx——优雅的CSS类名处理工具\"><a href=\"#Clsx——优雅的CSS类名处理工具\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Clsx——优雅的CSS类名处理工具\"></a>Clsx——优雅的CSS类名处理工具</h1><h2 id=\"简介\"><a href=\"#简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"简介\"></a>简介</h2><p>在前端开发中，处理CSS类名是一个常见的任务。尤其是在 React 等框架中，我们经常需要根据组件的状态动态生成类名。<code>clsx</code>是一个轻量级的库，可以帮助我们优雅地处理这些类名。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>A tiny (239B) utility for constructing className strings conditionally.<br>Also serves as a faster &amp; smaller drop-in replacement for the classnames module.<br>一个小巧（239B）的实用工具，用于有条件地构建类名字符串。也充当 classnames 模块的更快、更小的替代品。</p></blockquote>\n<p>这一模块有三种可用模式：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>ES Module</strong>: <code>dist/clsx.mjs</code></li>\n<li><strong>CommonJS</strong>: <code>dist/clsx.js</code></li>\n<li><strong>UMD</strong>: <code>dist/clsx.min.js</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装\"></a>安装</h2><figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install --save clsx</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"使用\"><a href=\"#使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用\"></a>使用</h2><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> clsx <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'clsx'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// or</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> { clsx } <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'clsx'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Strings (variadic) 字符串（可变参数）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>(<span class=\"string\">'foo'</span>, <span class=\"literal\">true</span> &amp;&amp; <span class=\"string\">'bar'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'baz'</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//=&gt; 'foo bar baz'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Objects 对象</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>({ <span class=\"attr\">foo</span>:<span class=\"literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"attr\">bar</span>:<span class=\"literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"attr\">baz</span>:<span class=\"title function_\">isTrue</span>() });</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//=&gt; 'foo baz'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Objects (variadic) 对象（可变参数）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>({ <span class=\"attr\">foo</span>:<span class=\"literal\">true</span> }, { <span class=\"attr\">bar</span>:<span class=\"literal\">false</span> }, <span class=\"literal\">null</span>, { <span class=\"string\">'--foobar'</span>:<span class=\"string\">'hello'</span> });</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//=&gt; 'foo --foobar'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Arrays 数组</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>([<span class=\"string\">'foo'</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"string\">'bar'</span>]);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//=&gt; 'foo bar'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Arrays (variadic) 数组（可变参数）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>([<span class=\"string\">'foo'</span>], [<span class=\"string\">''</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"string\">'bar'</span>], [[<span class=\"string\">'baz'</span>, [[<span class=\"string\">'hello'</span>], <span class=\"string\">'there'</span>]]]);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//=&gt; 'foo bar baz hello there'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Kitchen sink (with nesting) 综合使用（包含嵌套）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>(<span class=\"string\">'foo'</span>, [<span class=\"number\">1</span> &amp;&amp; <span class=\"string\">'bar'</span>, { <span class=\"attr\">baz</span>:<span class=\"literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"attr\">bat</span>:<span class=\"literal\">null</span> }, [<span class=\"string\">'hello'</span>, [<span class=\"string\">'world'</span>]]], <span class=\"string\">'cya'</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//=&gt; 'foo bar hello world cya'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"API\"><a href=\"#API\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"API\"></a>API</h2><h3 id=\"clsx-…input\"><a href=\"#clsx-…input\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"clsx(…input)\"></a>clsx(…input)</h3><p>返回值：<code>String</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"input\"><a href=\"#input\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"input\"></a>input</h3><p>类型：<code>Mixed</code></p>\n<p><code>clsx</code> 函数可以接受<strong>任意</strong>数量的参数，每个参数可以是对象、数组、布尔值或字符串。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>重要</strong>：任何‘假’值都会被丢弃！独立的布尔值也会被丢弃。</p></blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>(<span class=\"literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"string\">''</span>, <span class=\"literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"literal\">undefined</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"title class_\">NaN</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//=&gt; ''</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"效果对比\"><a href=\"#效果对比\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"效果对比\"></a>效果对比</h2><figure class=\"highlight jsx\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 不使用 clsx</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">MyComponent</span>(<span class=\"params\">{ isActive, className }</span>) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> classes = [</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'my-component'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    isActive ? <span class=\"string\">'active'</span> : <span class=\"string\">''</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    className || <span class=\"string\">''</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  ].<span class=\"title function_\">join</span>(<span class=\"string\">' '</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">trim</span>(); <span class=\"comment\">// 逻辑判断和处理不够优雅</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">className</span>=<span class=\"string\">{classes}</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-xml\">      Hello, World!</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-xml\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  );</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight jsx\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 使用 clsx</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> clsx <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'clsx'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">MyComponent</span>(<span class=\"params\">{ isActive, className }</span>) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> classes = <span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>(<span class=\"string\">'my-component'</span>, {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">active</span>: isActive,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    [className]: className</span><br><span class=\"line\">  });</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">className</span>=<span class=\"string\">{classes}</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-xml\">      Hello, World!</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-xml\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  );</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"版本\"><a href=\"#版本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"版本\"></a>版本</h2><p>有多种版本的 <code>clsx</code> 可用，这使您可以按需引入！</p>\n<h3 id=\"clsx\"><a href=\"#clsx\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"clsx\"></a>clsx</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" strok