>7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> { clsx } <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'clsx/lite'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// or</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> clsx <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'clsx/lite'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// string</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>(<span class=\"string\">'hello'</span>, <span class=\"literal\">true</span> &amp;&amp; <span class=\"string\">'foo'</span>, <span class=\"literal\">false</span> &amp;&amp; <span class=\"string\">'bar'</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// =&gt; \"hello foo\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// <span class=\"doctag\">NOTE:</span> Any non-string input(s) ignored</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clsx</span>({ <span class=\"attr\">foo</span>: <span class=\"literal\">true</span> });</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//=&gt; \"\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"支持\"><a href=\"#支持\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"支持\"></a>支持</h2><p>支持所有的 Node.js 版本。</p>\n<p>所有支持 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/isArray#Browser_compatibility\"><code>Array.isArray</code></a> 的浏览器（IE9+）都受支持。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5